cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the AMF IP address to an unreachable IP (192.168.70.133) will prevent NG interface connectivity, causing AMF attachment failures and configuration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Modifying the Ta4 timing parameters to [111, 181] introduces inconsistency in timing advance configuration, potentially causing synchronization issues, data transmission errors, and system faults in the DU.
